            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<ul><li>Fabric：95% Polyester / 5%Spandex</li><li>Texture: Snowflake </li><li>Weight: Lightweight</li><li>Stretch: 4-Way </li><li>Breathability: High</li><li>Moisture Management: Quick-Drying</li><li>Durability: Abrasion Resistant</li></ul>",
