            "heading": "Care",
            "icon": "none",
            "content": "<p>Move often. Care simply.</p><ul><li>Machine wash cold<br/></li><li>Wash with similar colors<br/></li><li>Turn inside out before washing<br/></li><li>Do not bleach<br/></li><li>Tumble dry low or line dry<br/></li><li>Do not iron<br/></li><li>Do not dry clean</li></ul><p>To preserve texture and performance, air drying is recommended.</p>",
