        "faq_i3m3aL": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "margin_top": 32,
            "margin_bottom": 32,
            "gap": 0,
            "faq_content": "<title>1. Is this shirt suitable for hot weather and travel?</title>\n<p>Yes. The snowflake-texture fabric is designed to improve airflow and wick moisture efficiently, helping keep you cooler and drier during movement, travel, and everyday wear.</p>\n<title>2. Will the fabric feel restrictive during activity?</title>\n<p>Not at all. The 5% spandex blend provides four-way stretch, allowing natural movement while maintaining a clean, close-to-body fit.</p>\n<title>3. Can I wear it for both outdoor and everyday use?</title>\n<p>Absolutely. Lightweight construction, breathability, and durable performance make it versatile enough for travel, commuting, light outdoor activities, and daily wear.</p>\n<title>4. Is it easy to care for?</title>\n<p>Yes. This shirt is machine washable and designed for low-maintenance wear. For best long-term performance, wash cold and air dry when possible.</p>\n<title>5.Does the fabric stay comfortable after sweating?</title>\n<p>Yes. The quick-drying construction helps move moisture away efficiently, while the breathable texture promotes airflow to reduce that heavy, damp feeling after activity.</p>",
            "target_tab": "faq"
          }
